reviews.review_text: A Trader's Favorite Always loved the unique song selection of set 1. Touch>Samson is also sweet. Nice to hear a clean copy after all this time!
9-21-82 Excellent both in sound quality and performance.

Perfect.  From the setlist to the recording to the performance this show is perfect. Anything less than five stars is an injustice. More proof that I was born too late, as if I weren't ten years old at the time I likely would have been at this show. :/

-q
